 Kapitel 2 und 3 unterstützen Unternehmen, die sich mit der weiterführenden Professionalisierung des Investitionscontrollings befassen, d. h. mit der Integration des Investitionscontrollings in ein SAP-System.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 15. Jun 2019) 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Accounting / General.2bisacsh1 aGerhards, Ralf, eauthor.1 aHoberg, Peter, eauthor.1 aWilms, Stefan, eauthor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG OWV ebook Paket Lehrbücher Wirtschaftswiss. 2018z9783110603262oZDB-23-OLW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2018z9783110603101oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831105780270 cprintz978311057790740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110577914423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110577914.jpg  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBVb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-OLWb2018